<DOCNO> APW19990318.0199 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-03-18 22:23:06 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<CATEGORY> sports </CATEGORY>
<HEADLINE> OHIO STATE 72, AUBURN 64 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 *Ohio St.-Auburn, Box    	
</P>
<P>
 *OHIO ST. (26-8)
</P>
<P>
        Brown 2-9 4-6 9, Singleton 3-4 1-3 7, Johnson 2-4 0-2 4, Penn  
9-16 4-4 26, Redd 9-19 3-4 22, Coleman 0-1 0-0 0, Savovic 1-3 0-0 2, 
Sanderson 0-2 0-1 0, Reese 1-4 0-3 2. Totals 27-62 12-23 72. 
AUBURN (29-4)
</P>
<P>
