<HEADLINE>  Amtrak 'Witness' Is Questioned </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	BOURBONNAIS, Ill. (AP) -- A potential witness has come forward  
who claims to have seen the crash of an Amtrak passenger train that 
rammed a truck, killing 11 people, an investigator said today. 
