<HEADLINE>  German Poet Had Remains Exhumed </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	BERLIN (AP) -- No one is more revered in German literature than  
Johann Wolfgang von Goethe, so it was with some surprise that a 
leading German newspaper broke the news Thursday that the national 
